        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Holding high-level Adobe certifications across Developer and Architect domains, ensuring every project follows industry best practices and optimal performance standards.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface-container border border-white/10 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
